														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1404386">
									

<p>One small detail bugs me. The log has a 173-second gap immediately followed by a 3 second gap. That doesn't make sense. That would just be a 176 second gap. If something happened that breaks up the 173 and the 3 (sounds of struggle, or a hum, or a recording malfunction for example), then it would be added as a note to the transcript. Otherwise the transcriber has no reason to break them up.</p>
<p>That's stupid, and more than a little OCD, for me to fixate on. But it is the one flaw I see in an otherwise very well done story.</p>

